2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper involves training a deep residual network to learn the dynamics of interacting shapes. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training a neural network with a quadratic loss. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper involves a physics simulator and deals with predicting the dynamics of objects. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with synthesizing images of 2D objects in motion.
